targets.formattedQuery: SELECT $timeSeries as t, count() FROM $table WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
targets.query:
$columns(
    'PSR %sat %freq',
    avg(psr) psr)
FROM $table
WHERE
    sat = '$satgraph'
    AND freq IN ($freq)
targets.rawQuery:
SELECT t, groupArray((concat('PSR ', sat, ' ', freq), psr)) AS groupArr FROM ( SELECT (intDiv(time, (1)) * (1)) AS t, sat, freq, avg(psr) psr FROM rawdata.range
WHERE "d" >= toDate(1665943068) AND "d" <= toDate(1665943968) AND time >= toUInt64(1665943068 * 1000) AND time <= toUInt64(1665943968 * 1000) AND
    sat = 'GLONASS1'
    AND freq IN ('L1CA') GROUP BY t, sat, freq ORDER BY t, sat, freq) GROUP BY t ORDER BY t

SELECT t, groupArray((concat('Perror ', sat, ' ', sigcomb), Perror)) AS groupArr FROM ( SELECT (intDiv(time, (1)) * (1)) AS t, sat, sigcomb, avg(Perror) Perror FROM computed.xz1
WHERE "d" >= toDate(1736600678) AND "d" <= toDate(1736600858) AND time >= toUInt64(1736600678 * 1000) AND time <= toUInt64(1736600858 * 1000) AND
    sat = 'GPS6'
    AND sigcomb IN ('L1CA+L2C','L1CA+L2P_codeless','L1CA+L5Q') GROUP BY t, sat, sigcomb ORDER BY t, sat, sigcomb) GROUP BY t ORDER BY t
